<h2 id="about" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">About</h2>
<p class="mb-2"> We completed Pre-Production in the 8 weeks prior to Production. The purpose was to establish structures to support and guide our team during Production. All team members worked 8-10 hours a week to create documents and timelines. </p>
<p> For more information about our Production process check out the <a class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-200" href="/game/prod/">Production Page</a>!</p>

